        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1204127938?book_show_action=true">Feb 18, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Steven Walle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Steven Walle" href="/user/show/37850168-steven-walle">Steven Walle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1204127938" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16406220658493085017">I have always loved this poem. This is argueabely the best poem ever written. This poem was composed by Virgil a poet from 29 BCE. I enjoyed this translation very much. I recommend this book to all.<br/>Enjoy and Be Blessed.<br/>Diamond</span>

